overview: Five Star Rapper is a track released on 13th of June 2022 by Quafff featuring Eliabu De King. It is Drill genred with good vibes and full of energy. The track was successfully accomplished due to the association of The Tragic Studio and Ashway Entertainment. Performed by Quafff and Eliabu De King, Five Star Rapper simply thanks all the fans, friends and families who have given support through out non stop.
title: Five Star Rapper
